{
  "stem": "23774.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they didn't know even what a Jew is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember when I landed in Italy, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I went up to Italians to tell them who I am.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I say, I'm a Juda.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't know what a Juda means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I'm Yid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't know, till months later they did find out that we have-- that we are Ebraici.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the word for a Jew, Ebraico.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they were OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Never had any problems there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just to go out with Italian girls, with Italian boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother left Italy to Canada from Genoa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to go to Genoa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to go to France, to Paris, because I thought, I'm going to Canada, so far.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll never have a chance to see Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So while I'm there, may as well see Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Rome, I went into the French consulate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tell them I'm going to Canada-- and I showed them my passport and my visa-- but I would like to visit France before I get.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, no problem.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the visa, I paid him-- I can't remember how much-- how much it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took the electric train, and I drove in-- we drove into-- to Paris.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spent a month in Paris.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was the Joint, the Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They help people that they didn't have any money or-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so we used to go there in the day times, sit, and read brochures from Israel, the newspaper, because they used to get Hebrew papers and Jewish paper.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I spent a month.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
